Why are you pissed?

315
00:25:18,560 --> 00:25:20,280
You’ll be frowning like a bulldog.

316
00:25:26,040 --> 00:25:28,680
Come on, Tintin. Let’s go to bed.

317
00:25:29,000 --> 00:25:31,000
So we don’t disturb him.

318
00:25:32,520 --> 00:25:33,520
Hold on.

319
00:25:35,040 --> 00:25:36,240
What now?

320
00:25:36,520 --> 00:25:38,360
You’re a girl.
How can you let a boy into your room?

321
00:25:40,040 --> 00:25:41,080
He’s a kid.

322
00:25:44,400 --> 00:25:45,720
Come on, you come sleep with me.

323
00:25:50,200 --> 00:25:52,960
