347
00:28:18,360 --> 00:28:20,840
Hey, look at this. Chocolate cake.

348
00:28:29,960 --> 00:28:35,440
Assumption number two,
your heart beats faster when she’s near.

349
00:28:35,640 --> 00:28:36,960
