354
00:29:05,520 --> 00:29:08,240
Come here, open your mouth.

355
00:29:10,800 --> 00:29:11,840
Is it good?

356
00:29:14,720 --> 00:29:18,200
Mom, let dad have a bite.

357
00:29:24,840 --> 00:29:26,920
He doesn’t like this flavor.

358
00:29:28,240 --> 00:29:29,960
It won’t hurt to try, will it?

359
00:29:35,600 --> 00:29:37,280
Excuse me, can I have another fork?

360
00:29:52,160 --> 00:29:53,080
It’s actually really good.

361
00:29:55,960 --> 00:29:58,260
Assumption number three,

