00:35:42,800 --> 00:35:44,960
- Hello.
- Come on in.

438
00:35:45,600 --> 00:35:50,340
- Oh Pupaa, both handsome and smart.
- Oh hello, Tookta.

439
00:35:50,340 --> 00:35:51,920
And also loves kids.

440
00:35:51,920 --> 00:35:53,840
He’s so perfect.

