00:36:14,360 --> 00:36:16,380
Otherwise,

446
00:36:16,380 --> 00:36:20,040
I wouldn’t dare to disturb them anymore.

447
00:36:21,280 --> 00:36:22,720
Next time,

448
00:36:25,480 --> 00:36:27,440
if you’re busy,
you can drop him off with us.

449
00:36:29,560 --> 00:36:31,000
Thank you.

450
00:36:32,000 --> 00:36:33,160
Here you go.

451
00:36:34,560 --> 00:36:35,560
I’ll get his shoes for you.

452
00:36:35,560 --> 00:36:36,440
Alright.

453
00:36:37,520 --> 00:36:38,240
Tintin.

