00:36:38,240 --> 00:36:39,600
Tintin, help me carry this.

455
00:36:40,040 --> 00:36:41,680
- I’ll head out now. Thank you.
- It’s alright.

456
00:36:41,680 --> 00:36:43,240
- Goodbye.
- Goodbye.

457
00:36:43,240 --> 00:36:45,320
Come on, son,
let’s get back to our room.

458
00:36:45,600 --> 00:36:46,840
Open the door.

459
00:36:46,840 --> 00:36:48,280
- Bye.
- Bye.

460
00:36:57,840 --> 00:36:59,360
Hello.

461
00:37:03,400 --> 00:37:04,720
That’s me.

462
00:37:05,400 --> 00:37:07,920
You’re interested in
being a creative worker, right?

463
00:37:09,720 --> 00:37:10,840
Yes.

464
00:37:11,840 --> 00:37:14,840
Alright. Then tomorrow at 10 a.m.

465
00:37:14,840 --> 00:37:15,880
Come in to talk to me.

466
00:37:16,560 --> 00:37:17,760
Bring your portfolio with you.

467
00:37:17,760 --> 00:37:19,840
I’ll send you the details via e-mail.

468
00:37:20,600 --> 00:37:23,360
Sure. See you tomorrow.

469
00:37:25,480 --> 00:37:28,160
Hey, I got a job.

470
00:37:28,160 --> 00:37:29,800
They called for an interview.

471
00:37:41,560 --> 00:37:46,240
So what do you want to eat today?
My treat.

472
00:37:48,640 --> 00:37:50,520
Anything will do.

