from zero, right?

481
00:38:37,160 --> 00:38:38,240
Learn everything,

482
00:38:38,240 --> 00:38:40,000
and work harder than others.

483
00:38:40,560 --> 00:38:42,120
Because you don’t have experience.

484
00:38:43,040 --> 00:38:44,160
I’m willing to learn.

485
00:38:44,160 --> 00:38:46,160
I’m willing to learn everything.

486
00:38:50,320 --> 00:38:52,600
Currently our department is very busy.

487
00:38:53,920 --> 00:38:56,320
We’ll work together through this.

488
00:38:59,040 --> 00:39:01,800
You’re taking me in already?

489
00:39:02,200 --> 00:39:03,200
Um.

490
00:39:03,960 --> 00:39:05,720
Really? Thank you so much.

491
00:39:05,720 --> 00:39:07,560
Thank you for giving me the opportunity.

492
00:39:08,320 --> 00:39:09,560
I’m so excited.

493
00:39:11,840 --> 00:39:12,880
I’m sorry.

494
00:39:12,880 --> 00:39:15,280
I was a little too excited.

495
00:39:15,280 --> 00:39:16,760
Thank you so much.

496
00:39:17,960 --> 00:39:19,760
