498
00:39:23,480 --> 00:39:24,880
Thank you, Faye.

499
00:39:24,880 --> 00:39:26,320
It’s alright. Work hard then.

500
00:39:26,600 --> 00:39:29,800
Yes, I’ll do my best.

501
00:39:37,540 --> 00:39:38,780
Yes.

502
00:39:44,800 --> 00:39:47,160
