509
00:40:25,800 --> 00:40:28,400
But I’m still doing more research.

510
00:40:30,840 --> 00:40:33,000
(Digital Holographic Interferometry)

511
00:40:34,560 --> 00:40:36,760
I didn’t mean the research topic.

512
00:40:36,760 --> 00:40:38,320
I meant your love story.

513
00:40:40,440 --> 00:40:43,240
I’m still in the process
of collecting data.

514
00:40:44,200 --> 00:40:48,880
But I’m not sure of the conclusion yet.

515
00:40:52,160 --> 00:40:55,400
You will have to keep collecting data.

516
00:40:55,400 --> 00:40:59,880
Do you need a hand?
It doesn’t look easy.

517
00:41:00,280 --> 00:41:02,600
I don’t think so.
I don’t think it’s that hard.

518
00:41:05,760 --> 00:41:07,840
I’m talking about the research topic.

519
00:41:08,760 --> 00:41:11,760
