526
00:41:37,240 --> 00:41:39,800
He’s my neighbor’s son.
She asked to babysit him.

527
00:41:42,120 --> 00:41:45,200
Then why were you with Pai yesterday?

528
00:41:45,200 --> 00:41:47,520
Or do you live together?

529
00:41:51,600 --> 00:41:54,600
Pai also knows Tintin,
so we went together.

530
00:41:54,840 --> 00:41:55,460
And,

531
00:41:55,460 --> 00:41:57,360
I’m not quite familiar
with being with kids.

532
00:41:58,800 --> 00:42:01,480
