534
00:42:03,920 --> 00:42:05,080
It looks cute.

535
00:42:06,240 --> 00:42:08,880
I’ll have to excuse myself.

536
00:42:09,560 --> 00:42:11,040
Professor, goodbye.

537
00:42:11,040 --> 00:42:12,160
Alright.

538
00:42:19,600 --> 00:42:21,360
I’ll just have to wait
until it’s cooked.

539
00:42:21,360 --> 00:42:22,960
Cooking isn’t that difficult.

540
00:43:12,680 --> 00:43:13,840
This way, please.

541
00:43:13,840 --> 00:43:23,280
Please gather around here.

542
00:43:38,560 --> 00:43:42,640
(Special scene)

543
00:43:44,240 --> 00:43:47,560
Hold on, why is this like this?

544
00:43:47,560 --> 00:43:49,920
This uniform is not good.

545
00:43:51,440 --> 00:43:52,960
Pupaa.

546
00:43:53,240 --> 00:43:56,800
- Yes, Tookta?
- Pai quit her job

547
00:43:56,800 --> 00:43:58,680
and she doesn’t have the money
to pay rent.

548
00:43:58,680 --> 00:44:00,080
Are you okay with that?

549
00:44:00,080 --> 00:44:01,760
But I don’t think I’m okay.

550
00:44:01,760 --> 00:44:05,160
She’s going to stay
without paying for anything at all.

551
00:44:05,160 --> 00:44:07,640
Isn’t she taking too much
advantage from us?

552
00:44:07,640 --> 00:44:08,760
I’m okay with it.

553
00:44:10,840 --> 00:44:13,440
I’ll let her stay with me
without paying yet.

554
00:44:14,160 --> 00:44:15,560
If I’m okay,

555
00:44:15,560 --> 00:44:17,200
then I don’t think
there should be any problem.

556
00:44:19,320 --> 00:44:22,320
The problem is I’m losing my income.

557
00:44:23,640 --> 00:44:26,760
Yay. Pai won’t get kicked out anymore.

558
00:44:27,880 --> 00:44:29,360
I have to go now.

